    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;olive oil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pat</strong> the fish dry&nbsp;and once the pan is hot, add the fish and cook for 2 min on both sides until starting to colour</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> each side with a pinch of salt (whilst in the pan)</p>",
